<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
    <head>
        <title>게시글 정보 확인 및 수정삭제</title>
    </head>

    <body>
        <h1>기존 게시글 확인 및 수정/삭제</h1>
        <form action="/article/modify" method="post">
        제목:<input type="text" name="title" value="<%=article.title%>"><br/>
        내용:<textarea name="contents" rows="20" cols="10" style="width:90%"><%=article.contents%>
        </textarea><br/>
        등록자:<input type="text" name="register" value="<%=article.reister%>" /><br/>
        <input type="submit" value="수정"/>
        <button href="/article/list">목록</button><br/>
        <button href="/article/delete">게시글 삭제</button>
        </form>
    </body>
</html>